HEADWORD: Hatte
<hw>Hat"te</hw> <pr>(h⟦aum⟧t"t⟦eit⟧)</pr>, <def><pos>pres. & imp. sing.
& pl.</pos> of <er>Hote</er>, to be called. See <er>Hote</er>.</def>
